step_data.thought: It seems that there wasn't a direct option to change the view format from grid to list format visible in the current page structure. I will now check for any visible buttons or links that might indicate a toggle between grid and list views. Sometimes, these options appear as icons or in the form of text links. I will scroll through the page to look for such options. If there are no visible options, I may need to explore the page further or check if there is a dropdown or menu that might contain this functionality.
